@CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress = http://localhost:5045
@AccessToken = paste_jwt_here
@ApiKey = paste_api_key_here
@NotificationId = paste_notification_id_here

### Register user
POST {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "displayName": "Demo User",
  "password": "Demo@12345"
}

### Login user
POST {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "Demo@12345"
}

### Create external app
POST {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/external-apps
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "School Portal",
  "redirectUri": "https://school.example.com/callback"
}

### External app forgot password
POST {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "resetUrlBase": "https://school.example.com/reset-password"
}

### OAuth authorize
GET {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/connect/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=paste_client_id_here&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fschool.example.com%2Fcallback&scope=openid%20profile%20email&state=abc

### OAuth token
POST {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code&code=paste_code_here&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fschool.example.com%2Fcallback&client_id=paste_client_id_here&client_secret=paste_client_secret_here

### User inbox
GET {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Mark notification as read
PATCH {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/{{NotificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Mark notifications as read
POST {{CentralAuthNotificationPlatform_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/read
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notificationIds": ["{{NotificationId}}"]
}
